➜重案公布：“台独”分子李孟居曾潜入深圳偷拍大量武警集结视频图片
http://www.sohu.com/a/423911425_162522	42729
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
